abel for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'41843\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_parent\' id=\'comment_parent\' value=\'0\' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="1c535e3d5a" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="6"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-due-foscari-al-teatro-real-di-madrid-con-placido-domingo/\' title=\'I due Foscari al Teatro Real di Madrid con Plcido Domingo\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Angela Meade, Placido Domingo, Michael Fabiano" title="I due Foscari al Teatro Real di Madrid con Plcido Domingo" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/opera-di-firenze-cortile-di-palazzo-pitti-la-traviata/\' title=\'Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="La traviata (prima) Simone Donati - TerraProject - Contrasto (10)" title="Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-puritani-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/\' title=\'I Puritani al Teatro Real di Madrid\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Madrid, Teatro Real, 11 VII 2016 (I Puritani) 8" title="I Puritani al Teatro Real di Madrid" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/roma-terme-di-caracalla-stagione-lirica-2016-nabucco/\' title=\'Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Nabucco_Il coro nel Va pensiero_Yasuko Kageyama-Opera di Roma, Caracalla 2016_7566" title="Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/staatsoper-stuttgart-i-puritani/\' title=\'Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="puritani, stuttgart, 2016" title="Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li></ul> </aside></div></div></div><div id="footer" role="contentinfo"><div class="container"><div class="row-fluid"><div class="span6"><div class="copyright-info"> Associazione Culturale GB Opera<br/>Sede legale: vicolo Scala Santa 6 - 37129 Verona<br/>Codice fiscale: 93238110238 - info@gbopera.it<br/> Pubblicazione ai sensi della legge n. 62 del 07.03.2001.<br/>Copyright  2008-2016</div></div><div class="span6"><div class="add-info"></div></div></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">jQuery.noConflict()(function($){$(document).ready(function(){var $container=$(\'#blog-entry\');$container.imagesLoaded(function(){$container.masonry({itemSelector:\'.masonry-box\',isAnimated:true,});});});});</script><script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function(){var q2w3_sidebar_1_options={"sidebar":"q2w3-default-sidebar","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0,"stop_id":"","screen_max_width":0,"width_inherit":false,"widgets":[\'mainmenu-block-bg\']};q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);setInterval(function(){q2w3_sidebar(q2w3_sidebar_1_options);},1500);});</script><script type=\'text/javascript\' src=\'http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/akismet/_inc/form.js\'></script><script type=\'text/javascript\'>var ajax_var={"url":"http:\\/\\/www.gbopera.it\\/wp-admin\\/admin-ajax.php","nonce":"8affa336e0"};</script><script type=\'text/javascript\'>var ct_localization={"go_to":"MENU"